summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing acquisition from King County of certain tax title property in Blocks 64, 70, 72, 73, 78, 79, 81, 83, 84, 85, 86, 87, 90, 91, 93, and 113 in Seattle Tide Lands and in Block 10, Minor's Addition for park, open space and recreation purposes and making an appropriation from the Emergency Fund therefor.
